{
 "name": "RPlog_Morganna_and_Rellik",
 "title": "Morganna and Rellik",
 "summary": "In a quiet starship lounge, the cruel Lord Rellik corners the scarred Ambassador Morganna Taszecks to debrief her and put her in her place. Demoted and humiliated, Morganna seethes as Rellik lords his authority over her, threatening her with a fate worse than the unfortunate Chantinelle Thistleborn and forcing her through degrading shows of obedience over a datacard of intelligence. Despite her barely-contained fury, she is compelled to accept a new assignment as intermediary to open negotiations with the Caspian government in exchange for the eventual return of her old position. Rellik dictates terms with relish, and a broken, raging Morganna submits before slinking out of the lounge.",
